Question: Are there either white cabinets or beds?

Reference Answer: no

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n499081.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='white cabinets')
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='beds')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX0)
ANSWER1=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} + {ANSWER1} > 0 else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
